SEARCH
Package research

Class ResearchProject

java.lang.Object
research.ResearchProject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ResearchProject extends Object implements Serializable
The ResearchProject class represents a research project in the system. It implements the Serializable interface to support serialization.
